document.title: NI 43-101 Technical Report for the Kinaskan Lake Project in North America dated May 2005.pdf
document.description: This technical report, prepared by consultants David T. Mehner and Giles R. Peatfield, provides an assessment of the Donnelly-GJ-North Copper-Gold Porphyry Zones in the Kinaskan Lake Project, including resource estimates and exploration recommendations.
